---
title: BP Agro — Flujo Sensor Node → Gateway → Aurora
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant SENS as 🔬 Sensores Suelo
    participant PI3 as 🖥️ Pi 3 Node
    participant GW as ⚙️ Farm Gateway
    participant DB as 🗄️ SQLite Local
    participant CHK as 🔍 Pre-check
    participant AUR as ☁️ AWS Aurora

    loop Cada 15 minutos
        SENS->>PI3: Lectura: humedad, pH, temp, NPK, EC
        PI3->>PI3: Valida rango de sensores
        PI3->>GW: POST /api/reading\n{machine_id, timestamp, valores}
        GW->>DB: INSERT reading (FCFS auto-increment)
        GW-->>PI3: ACK 200
    end

    loop Ciclo de upload (batch)
        GW->>DB: SELECT readings pendientes
        GW->>CHK: Query Aurora: ¿existe machine_id + timestamp?
        CHK->>AUR: SELECT WHERE machine_id AND timestamp IN (batch)
        AUR-->>CHK: Registros existentes
        CHK-->>GW: Filtrar duplicados
        GW->>AUR: INSERT solo registros nuevos
        AUR-->>GW: OK — rows inserted
        GW->>DB: Marcar como uploaded
    end
